   "body" : "It takes a while after running `bitcoind -daemon` before the process is ready to respond to rpc calls. And, from what I can tell, there's no to track progress. Instead, users of `bitcoin-cli` must repeat commands until the server responds.\r\n\r\nThis is a minor issue, of course, but it would be nice to have a progress bar to monitor the `bitcoind` server startup process.",
